WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:01.492
<i>Previously on "Shots Fired"...</i>

00:01.539 --> 00:03.210
The gun found in your office
was the same gun

00:03.273 --> 00:04.765
used to kill Joey Campbell.

00:04.813 --> 00:06.214
We had a break-in a few nights ago.

00:06.281 --> 00:08.216
Maybe that's when the gun was planted.

00:08.283 --> 00:10.117
Lieutenant Breeland found a witness

00:10.185 --> 00:11.752
who contradicted your theories

00:11.820 --> 00:13.788
regarding a link between
the Carr and Campbell shooting.

00:13.856 --> 00:16.041
Ruiz is prepping
a new team to take over.

00:16.111 --> 00:17.558
You both have a week to finish up.

00:17.626 --> 00:18.826
The gun used to kill Joey Campbell

00:18.894 --> 00:20.962
- is yours.
- It was stolen.

00:21.029 --> 00:24.065
Those two people are aiming
to blame that killing on me.

00:24.132 --> 00:25.700
ASHE: <i>Someone broke into our work space,</i>

00:25.767 --> 00:27.468
<i>sucker-punched me, and
I'm still mad about it.</i>

00:27.536 --> 00:29.776
They were after the video we
recovered off Jesse's phone.

00:29.837 --> 00:31.369
They don't have a video.
They're bluffing.

00:31.416 --> 00:32.363
Jesse didn't open his door.

00:32.430 --> 00:33.865
You pulled it open for him.

00:33.933 --> 00:36.086
I got your text. You're done
messing with my daughter.

00:36.111 --> 00:38.136
You were there when
Arlen Cox killed Joey.

00:38.204 --> 00:41.339
You ever want to be a mother
to your little girl again,

00:41.407 --> 00:43.608
you better start figuring out
what the word "smart" means.

00:44.110 --> 00:45.777
(both grunting)

00:45.845 --> 00:46.978
<i>I just lost Kai.</i>

00:47.046 --> 00:49.147
I killed somebody's child.
Why shouldn't I lose mine?

00:49.215 --> 00:50.549
Hey.

00:52.552 --> 00:53.985
ASHE: <i>Oh, my God, this is it.</i>

00:55.555 --> 00:56.555
<i>Check this out.</i>

01:04.629 --> 01:07.132
♪ <i>Oh</i> ♪

01:10.736 --> 01:14.172
♪ <i>Oh</i> ♪

01:14.240 --> 01:17.943
♪ <i>With your permission</i> ♪

01:18.010 --> 01:21.846
♪ <i>I just wanna spend a little time</i> ♪

01:21.914 --> 01:24.549
- (moaning)
- ♪ <i>With you</i> ♪

01:27.353 --> 01:31.356
♪ <i>With your permission</i> ♪

01:31.424 --> 01:36.094
♪ <i>Tonight I wanna be</i>
<i>a little me on you</i> ♪

01:36.162 --> 01:38.855
♪ <i>Oh, yeah, yeah ♪</i>

01:40.366 --> 01:44.169
♪ <i>With your permission</i> ♪

01:44.236 --> 01:46.504
♪ <i>I wanna spend the night</i>
<i>sipping on you</i> ♪

01:46.572 --> 01:49.174
I can't have you getting all sprung.

01:49.241 --> 01:51.276
I need you focused.

01:51.344 --> 01:53.278
Never been more focused in my life.

01:57.950 --> 02:01.553
The new team's arriving in two days.

02:01.621 --> 02:04.556
I don't want them messing up
what we started.

02:04.624 --> 02:07.258
Then let's finish it.

02:07.326 --> 02:09.461
You and me.

02:09.527 --> 02:12.897
REPORTER ON TV: <i>Breaking news report
regarding Jesse Carr's murder.</i>

02:12.965 --> 02:16.314
<i>The footage you're about to see
was uncovered on social media.</i>

02:16.836 --> 02:18.220
BECK: <i>What are you doing
in this neighborhood?</i>

02:18.314 --> 02:19.304
JESSE: <i>Why did you pull me over?</i>

02:19.587 --> 02:21.973
BECK: <i>Because you don't look right.</i>

02:22.041 --> 02:24.476
JESSE: <i>I didn't realize it was
illegal to be in this part of town.</i>

02:24.543 --> 02:26.945
BECK: <i>Depends on what you're doing here.</i>

02:27.013 --> 02:29.981
JESSE: <i>I came for some fried chicken.</i>

02:30.049 --> 02:31.282
You released it.

02:31.350 --> 02:33.318
I meant to send it to my account

02:33.386 --> 02:36.955
but I accidentally shared it
with Jesse's network.

02:37.023 --> 02:39.090
That's the story you're sellin'?

02:39.158 --> 02:40.325
Yeah.

02:40.393 --> 02:41.593
Right or wrong,

02:41.661 --> 02:43.595
there's no turning back now.
You know that.

02:45.197 --> 02:46.131
I know.

