<i>- I'm sorry, all right?
- Out of the car.</i>

03:19.131 --> 03:20.098
<i>Get out of the car!</i>

03:20.166 --> 03:22.500
(reporter speaking indistinctly)

03:22.568 --> 03:25.303
My son's last moments
now belong to the world.

03:30.676 --> 03:33.445
They have taken everything.

03:33.512 --> 03:35.517
Alicia...

03:35.783 --> 03:37.462
Alicia...

03:37.683 --> 03:39.494
Your memories of him,

03:39.652 --> 03:41.686
those are things between the two of you

03:41.754 --> 03:43.655
that ain't never gonna change.

03:43.723 --> 03:46.024
That the world can't touch.

03:46.092 --> 03:49.294
That's the truth you gonna hold on to.

03:49.361 --> 03:50.595
Not this.

03:56.235 --> 03:59.471
REPORTER: Sir... did you know
about the video, Sheriff?

03:59.538 --> 04:01.406
Does the department still
stand behind Deputy Beck?

04:01.474 --> 04:02.573
Will Beck finally be arrested?

04:02.629 --> 04:04.030
I know y'all are anxious for answers

04:04.105 --> 04:07.549
and, uh, I wish that I had them.

04:08.112 --> 04:11.026
We're just as surprised at this
latest development as you are.

04:11.057 --> 04:12.888
Any idea where the video came from?

04:12.947 --> 04:15.353
The department's spokesperson
will be releasing

04:15.447 --> 04:17.916
an official statement later today.

04:18.156 --> 04:20.925
I have no further comment
at this time. Thank you.

04:20.993 --> 04:22.594
How can your department support
a murderer?

04:29.201 --> 04:32.637
<i>Deputy Beck has been suspended.</i>

04:32.705 --> 04:35.173
<i>He is under a DOJ investigation.</i>

04:35.241 --> 04:37.575
<i>We are not supporting a murderer,</i>

04:37.643 --> 04:39.677
<i>we are supporting the legal process.</i>

04:39.745 --> 04:41.112
<i>Thank you.</i>

04:41.404 --> 04:43.681
- BREELAND: Tess, where are your sisters?
- They're coming.

04:43.749 --> 04:45.150
Y'all are gonna be late.

04:46.252 --> 04:47.986
Oh, my God, Daddy.

04:48.053 --> 04:50.588
It's nothing, I just got into it
with another cop last night.

04:50.656 --> 04:51.856
Are you okay?

04:51.924 --> 04:53.258
Yeah, it looks worse than it feels.

04:54.119 --> 04:56.694
Does that have anything to do
with that video on TV this morning?

04:56.762 --> 05:00.098
No, no, separate matter altogether.

05:00.166 --> 05:01.533
Hope the other guy looks worse.

05:04.488 --> 05:06.704
- Come on, girls.
- All right.

